snippet.title: Mambo - PlayStation 2 Gameplay
snippet.description:
Another CyberPlanet Interactive production on the PS2, with Phoenix Games publishing it as always, this is a puzzle game starring an elephant. This kinda feels like it would have been at home on Big Fish Games, but somehow got released on PlayStation 2 instead.
